<p>Crystals. Thanks a lot to the author of the Kalyson channel for the tutorial video: 
<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Pa5jdS5muz4" target="_blank" style="font-weight: bold; color: #1CAAD9;">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Pa5jdS5muz4</a><br /></p>

<p>The challenge is aimed at studying:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Program interface</li>
  <li>Functionality</li>
  <li>The main workflow</li>
  <li>Further application of materials in other programs</li>
</ul>

<p>Used programs:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Substance Designer</li>
  <li>Marmoset Toolbag 4</li>
  <li>Illustrator</li>
</ul>

